Waspinator got singed from the flame and used his right arm to black 
it from his face but was taking damage fast, he fired his gun at 
Grimlock with the other hand.

Quickstrike arrived at the battle site, he had run ahead of the rest 
of the group (OOC: I got tired of waiting for a reply from 
them) "Quickstrike terrorize" he exclaimed and transformed into robot 
mode "Now let's get to thrashing maxies" he said and fired a energy 
blast out of his snake head's mouth at Kup.

Kenzo landed and transformed into robot mode and waited to provide 
medical support for the maximals.
